<section id="testimonials" class="py-1">
<h2>Why this Baggage Tracking ?</h2>
<p>According to 2015 Global reports approximately 23.1 Million people are
facing problems with their luggage 6.1% People’s bags are getting stolen ,
14.8% bags are getting damaged and 79.1% people’s bags are getting delayed due
to various issues.So to abolish all the above problems there is a necessity
with this device</p>
<div class="testimonial bg-primary">
<img src="baggage1.jpeg" alt="No image">
<p>This baggage tracking app is an IoT(Internet of Things)
which is used to track your baggage with the help of IoT technology. The
location coordinates of the bag at a particular movement of time will be
stored and retrieved when the user puts a request to track the bag</p>
</div>
<div class="testimonial bg-primary">
<img src="baggage2.jpeg" alt="No image">
<p>Time saving process in tracking.Many times customers
struggle with very big queues and long waiting hours. Protection of your
lugagge with the presence of these kinds of device customers can completely
monitor and track their luggage Easy User Friendly service.Reduction in costs
by decreasing mishandled/lost/damaged bags</p>
</div>
